"{\"uid\": \"rte.ie-sport-paris-2024-2024-0605-1453235-the-fighting-is-just-in-us-barnes-olympic-double\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"RT\\u00c9 Sport multimedia journalist It's one thing to qualify for the Olympics but what about medalling at two separate games.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 123, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"one thing\", \"from\": 37, \"to\": 46}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 62, \"to\": 74}, {\"ngram\": \"two separate games\", \"from\": 103, \"to\": 121}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The first Irish boxer to do so was Belfast's Paddy Barnes, who claimed back-to-back bronze medals at Beijing 2008 and London 2012, going on to carry the Irish flag at the opening ceremony in Rio 2016.\", \"from\": 125, \"to\": 325, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 135, \"end\": 140, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"score\": 0.9997573946715439, \"rank\": 0.00021042077374660269, \"text\": \"Irish\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\"}, {\"begin\": 160, \"end\": 167, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belfast\", \"score\": 0.9999999999886313, \"rank\": 1.1256380933758208e-11, \"text\": \"Belfast\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belfast\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belfast\"}, {\"begin\": 170, \"end\": 182, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paddy_Barnes\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Paddy Barnes\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paddy_Barnes\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paddy_Barnes\"}, {\"begin\": 243, \"end\": 254, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2012_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.0520468133174218e-21, \"text\": \"London 2012\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2012_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2012_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 278, \"end\": 288, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Flag_of_Ireland\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Irish flag\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Flag_of_Ireland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Flag_of_Ireland\"}, {\"begin\": 316, \"end\": 319, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.999999999614829, \"rank\": 3.8499885308158973e-10, \"text\": \"Rio\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"back-to-back bronze medals\", \"from\": 196, \"to\": 222}, {\"ngram\": \"Beijing\", \"from\": 226, \"to\": 233}, {\"ngram\": \"the opening ceremony\", \"from\": 292, \"to\": 312}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Barnes also claimed a gold medal at the 2010 European Championships and silver in 2013 along with Commonwealth gold in 2010 and 2014.\", \"from\": 327, \"to\": 460, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 372, \"end\": 394, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UEFA_European_Championship\", \"score\": 0.9679871653707314, \"rank\": 0.03307154705619396, \"text\": \"European Championships\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UEFA_European_Championship\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UEFA_European_Championship\"}, {\"begin\": 425, \"end\": 437, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Commonwealth_Boxing_Council\", \"score\": 0.9926636522568363, \"rank\": 0.007390567516703804, \"text\": \"Commonwealth\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Commonwealth_Boxing_Council\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Commonwealth_Boxing_Council\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Barnes\", \"from\": 327, \"to\": 333}, {\"ngram\": \"a gold medal\", \"from\": 347, \"to\": 359}, {\"ngram\": \"silver\", \"from\": 399, \"to\": 405}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But it was not always smooth sailing for the Co Antrim boxer, who struggled in the early stages of his amateur career.\", \"from\": 462, \"to\": 580, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 510, \"end\": 516, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Antrim_GAA\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.5752913334276504e-17, \"text\": \"Antrim\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Antrim_GAA\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Antrim_GAA\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"smooth sailing\", \"from\": 484, \"to\": 498}, {\"ngram\": \"the early stages\", \"from\": 541, \"to\": 557}, {\"ngram\": \"his amateur career\", \"from\": 561, \"to\": 579}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"People make a big thing about it and I see why,\\\" Barnes tells Adrian Eames on Chapters of Magnificence, a new RT\\u00c9 Radio 1 series profiling 11 of Ireland's living Olympic medallists.\", \"from\": 582, \"to\": 764, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 728, \"end\": 735, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"score\": 0.9999325200719323, \"rank\": 6.367862723933965e-05, \"text\": \"Ireland\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"People\", \"from\": 583, \"to\": 589}, {\"ngram\": \"a big thing\", \"from\": 595, \"to\": 606}, {\"ngram\": \"Barnes\", \"from\": 632, \"to\": 638}, {\"ngram\": \"Adrian Eames\", \"from\": 645, \"to\": 657}, {\"ngram\": \"Chapters\", \"from\": 661, \"to\": 669}, {\"ngram\": \"Magnificence\", \"from\": 673, \"to\": 685}, {\"ngram\": \"a new RT\\u00c9 Radio 1 series\", \"from\": 687, \"to\": 711}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I lost my first 12 fights and people say would you not retire?\", \"from\": 766, \"to\": 829, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my first 12 fights\", \"from\": 774, \"to\": 792}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 797, \"to\": 803}]}, {\"sentence\": \"To be honest, most of them were pretty close and could have went either way and some of them I probably should have won.\\\"\", \"from\": 830, \"to\": 951, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Despite the early setbacks, Barnes remained positive and continued his push for success.\", \"from\": 953, \"to\": 1041, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 981, \"end\": 987, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sid_Barnes\", \"score\": 0.9999995288641204, \"rank\": 4.707955779694428e-07, \"text\": \"Barnes\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sid_Barnes\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sid_Barnes\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the early setbacks\", \"from\": 961, \"to\": 979}, {\"ngram\": \"his push\", \"from\": 1020, \"to\": 1028}, {\"ngram\": \"success\", \"from\": 1033, \"to\": 1040}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 37-year-old says: \\\"It shows that you will have many setbacks in life, whether it be in sport or business but if it's for you it will come, and it was obviously for me.\", \"from\": 1043, \"to\": 1214, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"many setbacks\", \"from\": 1094, \"to\": 1107}, {\"ngram\": \"life\", \"from\": 1111, \"to\": 1115}, {\"ngram\": \"sport\", \"from\": 1134, \"to\": 1139}, {\"ngram\": \"business\", \"from\": 1143, \"to\": 1151}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"After losing so much, then when I won, I became addicted to that feeling.\\\"\", \"from\": 1216, \"to\": 1291, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"that feeling\", \"from\": 1277, \"to\": 1289}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Off the back of defeat at the European Union Amateur Championships final in June 2008, Barnes was eager to make amends in Beijing just two months later.\", \"from\": 1293, \"to\": 1445, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1332, \"end\": 1337, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999874631052151, \"rank\": 1.2536072908999062e-05, \"text\": \"Union\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 1380, \"end\": 1386, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sid_Barnes\", \"score\": 0.9999995288641204, \"rank\": 4.707955779694428e-07, \"text\": \"Barnes\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sid_Barnes\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sid_Barnes\"}, {\"begin\": 1415, \"end\": 1422, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2008_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.02184967569162e-19, \"text\": \"Beijing\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2008_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2008_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the back\", \"from\": 1297, \"to\": 1305}, {\"ngram\": \"defeat\", \"from\": 1309, \"to\": 1315}, {\"ngram\": \"June\", \"from\": 1369, \"to\": 1373}, {\"ngram\": \"amends\", \"from\": 1405, \"to\": 1411}]}, {\"sentence\": \"With a bronze medal on the line, the 21-year-old light-flyweight was level with his Polish opponent after the first round of the quarter finals but pulled clear in the remaining three rounds to earn an 11-5 victory.\", \"from\": 1447, \"to\": 1662, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1531, \"end\": 1537, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Poland\", \"score\": 0.9911507823032295, \"rank\": 0.008462435659050723, \"text\": \"Polish\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Poland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Poland\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a bronze medal\", \"from\": 1452, \"to\": 1466}, {\"ngram\": \"the line\", \"from\": 1470, \"to\": 1478}, {\"ngram\": \"the 21-year-old light-flyweight\", \"from\": 1480, \"to\": 1511}, {\"ngram\": \"level\", \"from\": 1516, \"to\": 1521}, {\"ngram\": \"the first round\", \"from\": 1553, \"to\": 1568}, {\"ngram\": \"the quarter finals\", \"from\": 1572, \"to\": 1590}, {\"ngram\": \"the remaining three rounds\", \"from\": 1611, \"to\": 1637}, {\"ngram\": \"an 11-5 victory\", \"from\": 1646, \"to\": 1661}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He says: \\\"I never think of it, it's crazy!\", \"from\": 1664, \"to\": 1706, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I remember watching a video quite recently of me beating \\u0141ukasz Maszczyk from Poland for the medal, it was just amazing.\", \"from\": 1707, \"to\": 1827, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1764, \"end\": 1770, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/\\u0141ukasz_Konarzewski\", \"score\": 0.5031580251942751, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"\\u0141ukasz\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/\\u0141ukasz_Konarzewski\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/\\u0141ukasz_Konarzewski\"}, {\"begin\": 1785, \"end\": 1791, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Poland_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999063171255537, \"rank\": 9.369160834934987e-05, \"text\": \"Poland\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Poland_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Poland_national_football_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a video\", \"from\": 1727, \"to\": 1734}, {\"ngram\": \"the medal\", \"from\": 1796, \"to\": 1805}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was beyond my wildest dreams medalling at the Olympic Games.\", \"from\": 1828, \"to\": 1891, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my wildest dreams\", \"from\": 1842, \"to\": 1859}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic Games\", \"from\": 1873, \"to\": 1890}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Until you are there, you do not realise how big it is.\\\"\", \"from\": 1892, \"to\": 1947, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"That was Barnes' first medal and Ireland's first in Beijing.\", \"from\": 1949, \"to\": 2009, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1958, \"end\": 1964, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sid_Barnes\", \"score\": 0.9999995288641204, \"rank\": 4.707955779694428e-07, \"text\": \"Barnes\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sid_Barnes\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sid_Barnes\"}, {\"begin\": 1982, \"end\": 1989, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"score\": 0.9999325200719323, \"rank\": 6.367862723933965e-05, \"text\": \"Ireland\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\"}, {\"begin\": 2001, \"end\": 2008, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2008_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.02184967569162e-19, \"text\": \"Beijing\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2008_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2008_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But there was more than just a medal on Barnes' mind as he looked for revenge against Maszczyk.\", \"from\": 2011, \"to\": 2106, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2051, \"end\": 2057, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sid_Barnes\", \"score\": 0.9999995288641204, \"rank\": 4.707955779694428e-07, \"text\": \"Barnes\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sid_Barnes\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sid_Barnes\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"just a medal\", \"from\": 2035, \"to\": 2047}, {\"ngram\": \"revenge\", \"from\": 2081, \"to\": 2088}, {\"ngram\": \"Maszczyk\", \"from\": 2097, \"to\": 2105}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I fought that guy a year previous, and he beat me by 20 points.\", \"from\": 2108, \"to\": 2172, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"that guy\", \"from\": 2118, \"to\": 2126}, {\"ngram\": \"20 points\", \"from\": 2162, \"to\": 2171}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So just beating him for me was amazing, but the medal was the icing on the cake.\\\"\", \"from\": 2173, \"to\": 2254, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the medal\", \"from\": 2217, \"to\": 2226}, {\"ngram\": \"the icing\", \"from\": 2231, \"to\": 2240}, {\"ngram\": \"the cake\", \"from\": 2244, \"to\": 2252}]}, {\"sentence\": \"With a track record of great boxers being produced in Belfast, Barnes emphasised how growing up in the city made him stronger.\", \"from\": 2256, \"to\": 2382, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2310, \"end\": 2317, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belfast\", \"score\": 0.9999999999886313, \"rank\": 1.1256380933758208e-11, \"text\": \"Belfast\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belfast\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belfast\"}, {\"begin\": 2319, \"end\": 2325, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sid_Barnes\", \"score\": 0.9999995288641204, \"rank\": 4.707955779694428e-07, \"text\": \"Barnes\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sid_Barnes\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sid_Barnes\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a track record\", \"from\": 2261, \"to\": 2275}, {\"ngram\": \"great boxers\", \"from\": 2279, \"to\": 2291}, {\"ngram\": \"the city\", \"from\": 2355, \"to\": 2363}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Belfast is just a fighting city.\", \"from\": 2384, \"to\": 2417, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2385, \"end\": 2392, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belfast\", \"score\": 0.9999999999886313, \"rank\": 1.1256380933758208e-11, \"text\": \"Belfast\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belfast\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belfast\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"just a fighting city\", \"from\": 2396, \"to\": 2416}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You had to fight for everything.\\\"\", \"from\": 2418, \"to\": 2451, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"everything\", \"from\": 2439, \"to\": 2449}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He says: \\\"Whether it be human rights or civil rights, the fighting is just in us, and I think that's been shown on the international sporting stage.\\\"\", \"from\": 2453, \"to\": 2602, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"human rights\", \"from\": 2477, \"to\": 2489}, {\"ngram\": \"civil rights\", \"from\": 2493, \"to\": 2505}, {\"ngram\": \"the fighting\", \"from\": 2507, \"to\": 2519}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 2531, \"to\": 2533}, {\"ngram\": \"the international sporting stage\", \"from\": 2568, \"to\": 2600}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"A rich history of Commonwealth Games champions, European champions, professional world champions and Olympic medallists.\", \"from\": 2604, \"to\": 2725, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2623, \"end\": 2641, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Commonwealth_Games\", \"score\": 0.999310022895155, \"rank\": 0.0006820873296336192, \"text\": \"Commonwealth Games\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Commonwealth_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Commonwealth_Games\"}, {\"begin\": 2653, \"end\": 2671, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UEFA_European_Championship\", \"score\": 0.999755544763377, \"rank\": 0.00024404772398526259, \"text\": \"European champions\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UEFA_European_Championship\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UEFA_European_Championship\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"\\\"A rich history\", \"from\": 2604, \"to\": 2619}, {\"ngram\": \"professional world champions\", \"from\": 2673, \"to\": 2701}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympic medallists\", \"from\": 2706, \"to\": 2724}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We have not had an Olympic champion yet, but there is plenty of time for those to come.\\\"\", \"from\": 2726, \"to\": 2814, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an Olympic champion\", \"from\": 2742, \"to\": 2761}, {\"ngram\": \"plenty\", \"from\": 2780, \"to\": 2786}, {\"ngram\": \"time\", \"from\": 2790, \"to\": 2794}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Maybe I am lucky to have had had a such a figure in boxing as Gerry Storey when I was a kid.\", \"from\": 2816, \"to\": 2909, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2879, \"end\": 2891, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gerry_Storey\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Gerry Storey\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gerry_Storey\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gerry_Storey\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a such a figure\", \"from\": 2850, \"to\": 2865}, {\"ngram\": \"boxing\", \"from\": 2869, \"to\": 2875}, {\"ngram\": \"a kid\", \"from\": 2903, \"to\": 2908}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I might have had someone else, who did not take as great an interest in my career.\\\"\", \"from\": 2910, \"to\": 2993, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"someone\", \"from\": 2927, \"to\": 2934}, {\"ngram\": \"as great an interest\", \"from\": 2958, \"to\": 2978}, {\"ngram\": \"my career\", \"from\": 2982, \"to\": 2991}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Barnes admitted that unlike his team Ireland counterparts, he did not have a hero to aspire to but instead motivated himself.\", \"from\": 2995, \"to\": 3120, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3032, \"end\": 3039, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"score\": 0.9999325200719323, \"rank\": 6.367862723933965e-05, \"text\": \"Ireland\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Barnes\", \"from\": 2995, \"to\": 3001}, {\"ngram\": \"his team\", \"from\": 3023, \"to\": 3031}, {\"ngram\": \"a hero\", \"from\": 3070, \"to\": 3076}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I had no heroes whatsoever.\", \"from\": 3122, \"to\": 3150, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ng