em\", \"from\": 5277, \"to\": 5287}, {\"ngram\": \"the morning\", \"from\": 5336, \"to\": 5347}, {\"ngram\": \"the morning\", \"from\": 5370, \"to\": 5381}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I had never fought so close to a weigh-in in my life.\", \"from\": 5384, \"to\": 5438, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a weigh-in\", \"from\": 5416, \"to\": 5426}, {\"ngram\": \"my life\", \"from\": 5430, \"to\": 5437}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It told in the fight because after three seconds I had nothing left. \\\"\", \"from\": 5439, \"to\": 5509, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the fight\", \"from\": 5450, \"to\": 5459}, {\"ngram\": \"three seconds\", \"from\": 5474, \"to\": 5487}, {\"ngram\": \"nothing\", \"from\": 5494, \"to\": 5501}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Retiring in November 2019 after a rollercoaster of a career, Barnes remains in the history books as the first Irish boxer to win medals at two consecutive Olympic Games.\", \"from\": 5511, \"to\": 5680, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5572, \"end\": 5578, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sid_Barnes\", \"score\": 0.9999995288641204, \"rank\": 4.707955779694428e-07, \"text\": \"Barnes\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sid_Barnes\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sid_Barnes\"}, {\"begin\": 5621, \"end\": 5626, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"score\": 0.9997573946715439, \"rank\": 0.00021042077374660269, \"text\": \"Irish\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"November\", \"from\": 5523, \"to\": 5531}, {\"ngram\": \"a rollercoaster\", \"from\": 5543, \"to\": 5558}, {\"ngram\": \"a career\", \"from\": 5562, \"to\": 5570}, {\"ngram\": \"the history books\", \"from\": 5590, \"to\": 5607}, {\"ngram\": \"medals\", \"from\": 5640, \"to\": 5646}, {\"ng